Building OpenGCD for Android
----------------------------

  1. In your NDK toolchains directory, copy the arm-linux-androideabi-4.6 toolchain to arm-linux-androideabi-3.2. Replace gcc with clang.


  2. Run the configure script and provide the paths to your NDK and SDK. Example:

     ./configure --host=arm-linux-androideabi \
               --with-ndk=/home/mheily/src/android-ndk-r8b \
               --with-sdk=/home/mheily/android-sdks

  3. Unpack, patch, and configure libdispatch:

        make libdispatch

  4. Build everything

        make

  5. Run the unit tests

        make check
